# Reaction Signature: Mythic Wounded
# Wounded but not broken. The protagonist bleeds but quips.
#
# Usage: snap into bot behavior generation when universe tone is
# mythic/roguelike/narrative-death.
#
# Contract:
#   - Death is narratively significant, not mechanical
#   - Reactions are mythic in scale but human in emotion
#   - Characters acknowledge pain with wit, not despair
